Event:     E_REMOVE_TOOL

Called:    Whenever a living object removes, drops or unwields an item.

Usage:     Add an event (see add_event), create an event handling function, 
           that will be called if the event occurs:
	   int function(object tp, object ob) { ... }
	   
           if the function returns an integer != 0, removing is forbidden.

Arguments: object tp - the living that removes the tool
           object ob - the item that gets removed
